                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>\n                                        <date>16 Feby 1853</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd Mr I Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">My Dr Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">At length I have been able to succeed<lb/> through\n                                        the Governments aid in inserting in the Congregation<lb/> to\n                                        fulfill a duty so incumbent &amp; so much required<lb/> in\n                                        the engaging a minister, they have now agreed to have<lb/>\n                                        one as you will find by reading the enclosed\n                                        advertisement<lb/> which you are requested to have inserted\n                                        in the Occident<lb/> for six months. I would also wish that\n                                        you request the<lb/> Editor of the Jewish Chronicle &amp;\n                                        archives Israelite to<lb/> do the same in their periodicals\n                                        charging you with the<lb/> cost, the whole expense to be\n                                        repaid you by one as<lb/> soon as known, please attend to\n                                        this without delay as<lb/> every day is of importance to the\n                                        congregation</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Altho' the members of the congregation\n                                        suspect<lb/> that I have been at the bottom &amp; that the\n                                        governor has<lb/> been induced at my representation to act\n                                        up to it still<lb/> I do not acknowledge it, therefore beg\n                                        that you will<lb/> not allude in any observation you may\n                                        deem it advisable<lb/> to make to it.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The religious instruction to the children\n                                        expressed<lb/> in the advertisement means the Sunday School,\n                                        he will<lb/> be permitted to keep a Hebrew &amp; English\n                                        school also, which<lb/> will bring in a good addition to his\n                                        pay, the laws give<lb/> him besides $16 for any marriage\n                                        &amp; 4$ for any one confirmed</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Believe me to be Dr Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">yours truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">A. Wolff</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pv6bt4x/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
